<li id="cite_note-Jones-5"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Jones_5-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Jones_5-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Jones_5-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFLongueville_Jones1846" class="citation journal cs1"><a href="/wiki/Harry_Longueville_Jones" title="Harry Longueville Jones">Longueville Jones, Harry</a> (October 1846). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://archive.org/stream/archaeologiacam03powegoog#page/n554/mode/1up">"Mona Mediaeva No. IV"</a>. <i>Archaeologia Cambrensis</i>. <b>IV</b>. <a href="/wiki/Cambrian_Archaeological_Association" title="Cambrian Archaeological Association">Cambrian Archaeological Association</a>: 429–434<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">28 September</span> 2011</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Archaeologia+Cambrensis&amp;rft.atitle=Mona+Mediaeva+No.+IV&amp;rft.volume=IV&amp;rft.pages=429-434&amp;rft.date=1846-10&amp;rft.aulast=Longueville+Jones&amp;rft.aufirst=Harry&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Farchive.org%2Fstream%2Farchaeologiacam03powegoog%23page%2Fn554%2Fmode%2F1up&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ASt+Nidan%27s+Church%2C+Llanidan" class="Z3988"></span></span>
