<li id="cite_note-Sabine-8"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Sabine_8-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFBaring-GouldFisher,_John1907" class="citation book cs1"><a href="/wiki/Sabine_Baring-Gould" title="Sabine Baring-Gould">Baring-Gould, Sabine</a>; Fisher, John (1907). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://archive.org/details/cu31924092447816"><i>The lives of the British saints; the saints of Wales and Cornwall and such Irish saints as have dedications in Britain</i></a>. Vol.&#160;4. <a href="/wiki/Honourable_Society_of_Cymmrodorion" title="Honourable Society of Cymmrodorion">Honourable Society of Cymmrodorion</a>. pp.&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://archive.org/details/cu31924092447816/page/n21">14</a>–16.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+lives+of+the+British+saints%3B+the+saints+of+Wales+and+Cornwall+and+such+Irish+saints+as+have+dedications+in+Britain&amp;rft.pages=14-16&amp;rft.pub=Honourable+Society+of+Cymmrodorion&amp;rft.date=1907&amp;rft.aulast=Baring-Gould&amp;rft.aufirst=Sabine&amp;rft.au=Fisher%2C+John&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Farchive.org%2Fdetails%2Fcu31924092447816&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ASt+Nidan%27s+Church%2C+Llanidan" class="Z3988"></span></span>
</li>
